	<div id="who-can-use"></div>
	<h2>Who can use RMap?</h2>
	<p>Anyone can view RMap data either through the open API, or by navigating the data in the <a href="<c:url value='/home'/>">visual website</a>.
	The policies around writing data to RMap may vary by institution. 
