	In this instance of RMap, anyone with a <a href="https://google.com">Google</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com">Twitter</a>, or <a href="https://orcid.org">ORCID</a> account can <a href="<c:url value='/user/login'/>">log in</a> and create keys that provide write access to the RMap API. All data created through the API is immediately available through the public API and visual website.</p>
